<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.3">
<l>paṉmaṇi muttiṉ pavaḷam patittaṉṉa</l>
<l>veṉmaṇi vaṇṇa ṉilaṅkupoṟ ṟōṭṭiṉmēl</l>
<l>niṉmaṇi vāymut tilaṅkaniṉ ṉammaita</l>
<l>ṉammaṉi mēṟkoṭṭāy cappāṇi yāḻiyaṅkaiyaṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My sapphire hued [child], clap cappāṇi upon the waist of your mother</l>
<l>so that [your] pearls shine in your ruby mouth, with shining gold leaf earrings above,</l>
<l>like many gems and pearls inlayed in pleasing coral!</l>
<l>You whose hands [bear] the discus, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
